snippet.title: Projekt Z: Beyond Order – Console Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Battle the undead in this thrilling First-Person Zombie Shooter with robust character progression and weapon customization. Set around World War II, take on fast-paced missions as one of four survivors, each with their own unique abilities and role in 4-player Co-op.

Wishlist now: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/projekt-z-beyond-order/9MXJ58HPTXQZ
